<hr data-start="211" data-end="214">
<h2 data-section-id="3n56e3" data-start="216" data-end="255">🌟 1. Hero Section (Services Banner)</h2>
<p data-start="256" data-end="282">A strong intro at the top.</p>
<p data-start="284" data-end="301"><strong data-start="284" data-end="301">Content idea:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="302" data-end="442">
<li data-section-id="1ch13x0" data-start="302" data-end="325">
<p data-start="304" data-end="325">Title: <em data-start="311" data-end="325">Our Services</em></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="10ictev" data-start="326" data-end="394">
<p data-start="328" data-end="394">Short tagline: <em data-start="343" data-end="394">“Train, Perform &amp; Express Yourself Through Dance”</em></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="i3nppm" data-start="395" data-end="442">
<p data-start="397" data-end="442">Background image (dance performance / studio)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="444" data-end="447">
<h2 data-section-id="6pfgt7" data-start="449" data-end="479">💃 2. Dance Classes Section</h2>
<p data-start="480" data-end="506">Show all styles you teach.</p>
<p data-start="508" data-end="531"><strong data-start="508" data-end="531">Include cards like:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="532" data-end="617">
<li data-section-id="1ezl1u3" data-start="532" data-end="547">
<p data-start="534" data-end="547">Bharatanatyam</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="o8jg2r" data-start="548" data-end="557">
<p data-start="550" data-end="557">Hip-Hop</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1hmq3m9" data-start="558" data-end="572">
<p data-start="560" data-end="572">Contemporary</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="109doiq" data-start="573" data-end="590">
<p data-start="575" data-end="590">Bollywood Dance</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1bab3gs" data-start="591" data-end="617">
<p data-start="593" data-end="617">Classical Dance Training</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="619" data-end="638">Each card can have:</p>
<ul data-start="639" data-end="711">
<li data-section-id="16t8r8v" data-start="639" data-end="646">
<p data-start="641" data-end="646">Image</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="q1gf3w" data-start="647" data-end="666">
<p data-start="649" data-end="666">Short description</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="on2ib2" data-start="667" data-end="711">
<p data-start="669" data-end="711">Level (Beginner / Intermediate / Advanced)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="713" data-end="716">
<h2 data-section-id="n28kw0" data-start="718" data-end="751">🏆 3. Private Coaching Section</h2>
<p data-start="752" data-end="778">Personal training details.</p>
<p data-start="780" data-end="792"><strong data-start="780" data-end="792">Content:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="793" data-end="882">
<li data-section-id="1iqhc39" data-start="793" data-end="810">
<p data-start="795" data-end="810">1-to-1 coaching</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="du4iny" data-start="811" data-end="829">
<p data-start="813" data-end="829">Flexible timings</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1r306x7" data-start="830" data-end="857">
<p data-start="832" data-end="857">Personalized choreography</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1uay2sb" data-start="858" data-end="882">
<p data-start="860" data-end="882">Fast learning programs</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="884" data-end="887">
<h2 data-section-id="rx72u7" data-start="889" data-end="926">🎭 4. Performance Training Section</h2>
<p data-start="927" data-end="949">For stage preparation.</p>
<p data-start="951" data-end="963"><strong data-start="951" data-end="963">Include:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="964" data-end="1074">
<li data-section-id="1keqa33" data-start="964" data-end="992">
<p data-start="966" data-end="992">Stage performance practice</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="dhthel" data-start="993" data-end="1015">
<p data-start="995" data-end="1015">Competition training</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1a8zvmi" data-start="1016" data-end="1037">
<p data-start="1018" data-end="1037">Confidence building</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="155pjjc" data-start="1038" data-end="1074">
<p data-start="1040" data-end="1074">Expression &amp; technique improvement</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1076" data-end="1079">
<h2 data-section-id="18hnfjk" data-start="1081" data-end="1116">👶 5. Kids Dance Program Section</h2>
<p data-start="1117" data-end="1146">Special section for children.</p>
<p data-start="1148" data-end="1160"><strong data-start="1148" data-end="1160">Content:</strong></p>
<ul data-start="1161" data-end="1264">
<li data-section-id="1q2e5n8" data-start="1161" data-end="1187">
<p data-start="1163" data-end="1187">Fun learning environment</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1a699r9" data-start="1188" data-end="1222">
<p data-start="1190" data-end="1222">Basic rhythm &amp; movement training</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ec62ho" data-start="1223" data-end="1241">
<p data-start="1225" data-end="1241">Group activities</p>
